[SPEAKER_12]: Councilor Behrs.

143
00:11:54,451 --> 00:11:55,231
[SPEAKER_08]: Thank you, Madam President.

144
00:11:56,272 --> 00:12:16,199
[SPEAKER_08]: I would move to request that the Office of Planning, Development and Sustainability send a short draft for review by the Council of a PDD fee at five cents per square foot for any project greater than 5,000 square feet.

145
