[SPEAKER_00]: So what I suggest to add is,

745
01:01:07,065 --> 01:01:21,706
[SPEAKER_00]: at the end of section 3.1 point one at the following at the end of the paragraph, however, the building commissioner may determine like uses deemed to be similar in nature, with assistance from the planning director, and I say that because

746
01:01:23,037 --> 01:01:29,722
