747
01:01:31,123 --> 01:01:41,551
[SPEAKER_00]: If the building commissioner, you know, me or whoever's in the future has a problem with determination, if it's not exactly identified and uses change all the time, new uses come up all the time.

748
01:01:41,611 --> 01:01:49,197
[SPEAKER_00]: One of the latest ones is the panic room, the game room where you go in and you, you know, you have this room and you've got to figure out how to get out of this room.

749
01:01:49,718 --> 01:01:51,539
[SPEAKER_00]: There's nothing in any zoning ordinance for that.

750
01:01:52,780 --> 01:01:52,980
[SPEAKER_00]: Right.

751
01:01:53,040 --> 01:01:53,240
[SPEAKER_00]: Yeah.

752
01:01:53,280 --> 01:01:54,221
[SPEAKER_00]: Well, I call it a panic.

753
01:01:54,261 --> 01:01:55,262
[SPEAKER_00]: I call it a panic room.

754
01:01:55,302 --> 01:01:59,164
[SPEAKER_00]: But what it is, is, you know, you have this game where, you know, it's like, you don't know.

755
01:01:59,344 --> 01:01:59,684
[SPEAKER_00]: Yeah.

756
01:01:59,704 --> 01:02:02,586
[SPEAKER_00]: The rocket's going to launch off if you don't kill the countdown.

757
01:02:02,626 --> 01:02:04,187
[SPEAKER_00]: You know, you got to figure out how to kill the countdown.

758
01:02:04,607 --> 01:02:07,009
[SPEAKER_00]: You know, these kinds of uses are they entertain?

759
01:02:07,029 --> 01:02:08,129
[SPEAKER_00]: Are they amusement uses?

760
01:02:08,249 --> 01:02:09,350
[SPEAKER_00]: Are they arcade uses?

761
01:02:09,470 --> 01:02:11,892
[SPEAKER_00]: Are they, you know, are they inside game room?

762
01:02:11,932 --> 01:02:14,073
[SPEAKER_00]: I mean, they're very hard to define, you know.

763
01:02:15,053 --> 01:02:16,934
[SPEAKER_00]: You know, a simple thing like an art studio.

764
01:02:17,135 --> 01:02:22,938
[SPEAKER_00]: I had a person who wanted to open up a coloring book room and there was nothing in the zoning ordinance for it.

765
01:02:22,958 --> 01:02:23,438
[SPEAKER_00]: What am I going to do?

766
01:02:23,798 --> 01:02:25,879
[SPEAKER_00]: Say no and crush everybody's fund?

767
