[SPEAKER_00]: If you're sitting next to one every day and all you smell is yeast, it's disgusting.

792
01:05:05,370 --> 01:05:08,212
[SPEAKER_00]: You know, and so those, you know, same with a microbrewery.

793
01:05:08,252 --> 01:05:10,633
[SPEAKER_00]: Microbreweries have a tendency to generate odor.

794
01:05:10,773 --> 01:05:11,814
[SPEAKER_08]: That sounds, sounds great.

795
01:05:11,854 --> 01:05:15,816
[SPEAKER_08]: I'm just, so, so odor, fumes, or electric time, electromagnetic transmission, you added.

796
01:05:16,257 --> 01:05:20,459
