858
01:11:53,667 --> 01:12:02,435
[SPEAKER_05]: And we could ask them each time we say, we have this project, can you give us a quote for how much time do you think this will be, provide us with that.

859
01:12:03,271 --> 01:12:08,279
[SPEAKER_05]: And I think that that process would serve us well, because we could qualify them for three years.

860
